Fri Apr 17 12:00:00 UTC 2026 - Alessio Biancalana <dottorblaster@opensuse.org>

- Initial package of noctalia-qs 0.0.4.
  noctalia-qs is a fork of Quickshell maintained by the Noctalia
  project, adding shell-specific Wayland protocols (most notably
  ext-background-effect-v1) on top of upstream Quickshell.
- The binary is a drop-in replacement for quickshell, so the
  package declares Provides: quickshell and Conflicts: quickshell.

